83a7abf5-9f9f-4d46-a383-2b425b960f7f.title: <player>
83a7abf5-9f9f-4d46-a383-2b425b960f7f.text: I am here to help you free the prince.

642ae7e4-3b56-497b-89d4-b98e4b618679.title: Leela
642ae7e4-3b56-497b-89d4-b98e4b618679.text:
Your employment is known to me. Now, do you know
all that we need to make the break?

options.text: I must make a disguise. What do you suggest?
I need to get the key made.
What can I do with the guards?
I will go and get the rest of the escape equipment.

1717deb1-b7e7-434a-8874-f2460c019e28.title: <player>
1717deb1-b7e7-434a-8874-f2460c019e28.text: I must make a disguise. What do you suggest?

f1cf102b-bb26-43e8-9b68-e36e125b43a9.title: Leela
f1cf102b-bb26-43e8-9b68-e36e125b43a9.text:
Only the lady Keli, can wander about outside the jail.
The guards will shoot to kill if they see the prince out
so we need a disguise good enough to fool them at a
distance.

e3fbe91f-ed67-49fb-a7b2-03015da098f6.title: Leela
e3fbe91f-ed67-49fb-a7b2-03015da098f6.text:
You need a wig, maybe made from wool. If you find
someone who can work with wool ask them about it.
There's a witch nearby may be able to help you dye it.

44b76f2e-e9d8-410b-b1ca-b60a112ff770.title: Leela
44b76f2e-e9d8-410b-b1ca-b60a112ff770.text: You will need to get a pink skirt, same as Keli's.

d7b00c96-a780-4c69-94b2-0d30cf873498.title: Leela
d7b00c96-a780-4c69-94b2-0d30cf873498.text:
We still need something to colour the Prince's skin
lighter. There's a witch close to here. She knows about
many things. She may know some way to make the
skin lighter.

7dbef658-d466-4d3d-9f6f-ea6ae7654bb5.title: Leela
7dbef658-d466-4d3d-9f6f-ea6ae7654bb5.text:
You will still need some rope to tie up Keli, of course. I
heard that there's a good rope maker around here.

options.text: I need to get the key made.
What can I do with the guards?
I will go and get the rest of the escape equipment.

7319b771-7c11-4845-8830-358e7ea2795b.title: <player>
7319b771-7c11-4845-8830-358e7ea2795b.text: I need to get the key made.

d78db616-337f-4d39-ad4e-48f63568f6b5.title: Leela
d78db616-337f-4d39-ad4e-48f63568f6b5.text:
Yes, that is most important. There is no way you can
get the real key. It is on a chain around Keli's neck.
Almost impossible to steal.

5146b8db-3faa-453e-8c0a-a46fff03067f.title: <player>
5146b8db-3faa-453e-8c0a-a46fff03067f.text:
Get some soft clay and get her to show you the key
somehow. Then take the print, with bronze, to my
father.

options.text: I must make a disguise. What do you suggest?
What can I do with the guards?
I will go and get the rest of the escape equipment.

75451f2c-0087-4416-be66-fd89fbe60c49.title: <player>
75451f2c-0087-4416-be66-fd89fbe60c49.text: What can I do with the guards?

64b55748-58de-45f4-8014-9f826388f680.title: Leela
64b55748-58de-45f4-8014-9f826388f680.text:
Most of the guards will be easy. The disguise will get
past them. The only guard who will be a problem will be
the one at the door.

514a2718-76cc-4539-9a4c-839a62dffabc.title: Leela
514a2718-76cc-4539-9a4c-839a62dffabc.text:
We can discuss this more when you have the rest of
the escape kit.

33ced4f1-29c5-4ebb-b26f-327533240d43.title: Missing
33ced4f1-29c5-4ebb-b26f-327533240d43.text: Dialogue if you have all the items?

options.text: I must make a disguise. What do you suggest?
I need to get the key made.
I will go and get the rest of the escape equipment.

1973cffa-8b86-4119-90c7-0b08cb1f5274.title: <player>
1973cffa-8b86-4119-90c7-0b08cb1f5274.text: I will go and get the rest of the escape equipment.

725ad7da-f216-49c0-b4b1-2cb656c783b5.title: Leela
725ad7da-f216-49c0-b4b1-2cb656c783b5.text: Good, I shall await your return with everything.

fc7cd12c-8981-4f2c-b221-61dad47ed971.title: Untitled
fc7cd12c-8981-4f2c-b221-61dad47ed971.text:
Good, you have all the basic equipment. Next to deal
with the guard on the door. He is talkative, try to find
a weakness in him.

e3506e88-59e5-4863-bd5b-640ee6191377.title: Leela
e3506e88-59e5-4863-bd5b-640ee6191377.text:
My father sent this key for you.
Be careful not to lose it.
